  "description": "<i>Actua Golf 3</i> is a golf simulation game featuring eight courses. You can completely customize your own character. With a new character you start with amateur tournaments until you have removed your handicap. Then you can participate in the pro tournaments.<br><br>To hit the ball in this game the player will have to use his analogue stick and swing that much like a real club.<br><br>The game features commentary by <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/developer/sheet/view/developerId,24386/\">Peter Alliss</a> and <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/developer/sheet/view/developerId,176253/\">Alex Hay</a>.",
